WEBVTT

01:39.410 --> 01:43.620
[Road to Success]

01:44.600 --> 01:47.940
[Episode 22]

01:48.200 --> 01:49.580
Let's check with the doctor again.

01:49.580 --> 01:50.000
Mom.

01:52.789 --> 01:53.720
How's your foot,

01:54.120 --> 01:54.680
Fu?

01:55.039 --> 01:56.300
Are you okay, Captain?

01:56.590 --> 01:57.710
Don't worry, everyone.

01:57.710 --> 02:00.350
The doctor said
it should just be a soft tissue injury.

02:00.350 --> 02:02.000
We're waiting for a CT scan

02:02.000 --> 02:04.260
to make sure there aren't any fractures.

02:04.280 --> 02:05.410
That Wen Chengye...

02:06.950 --> 02:08.960
We never should've asked him to come.

02:08.960 --> 02:10.949
He really never changes.

02:12.840 --> 02:13.400
Ms. Lin.

02:14.800 --> 02:16.660
What are we going to do from now on?

02:19.840 --> 02:20.840
Do you mean

02:21.280 --> 02:22.280
what you should do

02:22.680 --> 02:24.810
or what we should do about Wen Chengye?

02:25.079 --> 02:25.840
The latter.

02:28.360 --> 02:30.960
I don't want to
play football with him anymore.

02:31.470 --> 02:32.730
He's not a good person.

02:36.130 --> 02:37.110
Zhi Hui,

02:37.870 --> 02:39.190
that's a bit too harsh.

02:39.590 --> 02:40.450
Don't say that.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.560
Then why didn't he apologize

02:41.560 --> 02:42.560
after what he did?

02:45.630 --> 02:47.030
I think he's just indifferent

02:47.030 --> 02:48.440
to all of us equally.

02:49.030 --> 02:50.960
That's why he acted so recklessly,

02:51.120 --> 02:53.720
without caring about
the consequences at all.

02:56.850 --> 02:58.910
I don't want to play with him anymore.

02:59.230 --> 03:00.580
Neither do I.

03:00.210 --> 03:04.630
[Inpatient Building]

03:01.070 --> 03:02.450
Me neither.

03:02.640 --> 03:03.840
Me neither.

03:09.170 --> 03:10.540
He isn't happy on this team,

03:10.540 --> 03:12.470
and he doesn't want to be part of it.

03:13.190 --> 03:16.190
Maybe we shouldn't have forced him
in the first place.

03:19.230 --> 03:20.700
As if I care about you guys!

03:24.680 --> 03:26.590
A bunch of brain-dead

03:26.590 --> 03:27.980
football scrubs.

03:28.240 --> 03:29.150
What did you say?

03:29.150 --> 03:29.590
Qin Ao!

03:29.590 --> 03:31.000
-Look at his attitude!
-Exactly!

03:31.000 --> 03:31.960
Fu Xinshu.

03:32.710 --> 03:33.190
I'll handle this.

03:33.190 --> 03:34.720
You go check on Wen Chengye.

03:42.440 --> 03:43.300
Wen Chengye!

03:47.630 --> 03:48.230
I'm fine.

03:48.370 --> 03:49.560
Ms. Lin, you can go back.

03:49.560 --> 03:51.020
I'm your team supervisor.

03:51.190 --> 03:52.990
I can't let you go off on your own.

03:53.310 --> 03:53.800
Team?

03:54.840 --> 03:55.750
What team?

03:57.030 --> 03:58.760
They've already abandoned me.

04:05.480 --> 04:06.220
Don't worry.

04:06.240 --> 04:08.560
I can take the high-speed train back
by myself.

04:08.560 --> 04:09.120
No.

04:09.200 --> 04:10.400
That's too dangerous.

04:10.400 --> 04:11.300
Ms. Lin,

04:11.960 --> 04:12.800
I'll be fine.

04:15.470 --> 04:17.000
You should go back, Ms. Lin.

04:26.080 --> 04:27.120
How is he?

04:27.660 --> 04:29.160
The doctor checked the scans

04:29.160 --> 04:31.290
and said he'll be fine after some rest.

04:31.950 --> 04:32.630
That's a relief.

04:32.630 --> 04:34.750
Fu, I'll have you over
for fried skewers later

04:34.750 --> 04:35.750
to help you recover.

04:35.750 --> 04:37.040
You'll carry Fu there?

04:37.040 --> 04:38.360
I'm buying, you're carrying.

04:38.360 --> 04:38.990
Deal.

04:39.270 --> 04:40.159
Fu Xinshu,

04:40.159 --> 04:40.920
how did it go?

04:41.390 --> 04:42.240
Ms. Lin,

04:42.240 --> 04:43.040
I'm fine.

04:43.720 --> 04:44.920
Where's Wen Chengye?

04:45.600 --> 04:46.860
Why bother asking him?

04:48.270 --> 04:50.800
He took the high-speed train back
by himself.

04:53.270 --> 04:54.390
It's getting late.

04:54.390 --> 04:55.720
We should head back too.

04:56.480 --> 04:57.480
I'll do it, Coach.

05:16.120 --> 05:16.750
Ms. Lin.

05:18.400 --> 05:20.430
Are we still going to
keep playing football?

05:20.430 --> 05:21.760
What makes you ask that?

05:22.120 --> 05:23.680
You've lost one match,

05:23.680 --> 05:25.240
but there are
still plenty more games ahead.

05:25.240 --> 05:26.770
But we're down a player now.

05:27.270 --> 05:29.200
Can we still call ourselves a team?

05:30.360 --> 05:32.110
We got hammered 11–0.

05:32.110 --> 05:33.190
Could it be that

05:34.159 --> 05:35.960
we just don't have what it takes?

05:38.460 --> 05:39.820
I hate to admit it,

05:41.159 --> 05:42.680
but we really suck.

05:42.920 --> 05:44.120
An uncertain future—

05:44.830 --> 05:45.560
a bad omen.

05:49.190 --> 05:50.650
Is that how all of you feel?

05:52.390 --> 05:53.600
What else can we do?

05:54.920 --> 05:56.920
We have to face reality eventually.

05:58.830 --> 05:59.680
I disagree.

06:00.600 --> 06:02.270
Of course, we have to keep playing.

06:02.270 --> 06:03.360
Not only that,

06:03.680 --> 06:05.310
we also have to crush Yongchuan Hengjiu.

06:05.310 --> 06:05.950
Right?

06:19.040 --> 06:19.510
Come on.

06:20.040 --> 06:21.190
Am I wrong?

06:21.600 --> 06:22.390
No.

06:27.240 --> 06:29.160
Boys, cheer up.

06:29.430 --> 06:31.190
You still have me.

06:31.480 --> 06:32.360
And Coach.

06:32.680 --> 06:34.140
With a coach this amazing,

06:34.240 --> 06:35.630
we'll get there.

06:43.040 --> 06:43.680
Right?

06:45.680 --> 06:46.270
Right.

06:54.430 --> 06:55.120
Alright.

06:55.390 --> 06:56.830
We've still got more than two hours to go.

06:56.830 --> 06:58.120
Get some sleep first.

06:59.120 --> 07:01.160
Driver, please turn off the lights.

07:02.830 --> 07:03.760
Let's all sleep.

07:04.240 --> 07:05.700
What else can we do anyway?

07:27.550 --> 07:32.490
[Wen Chengye]

07:27.720 --> 07:30.040
Wen, have you boarded the train?

07:30.510 --> 07:31.190
Yeah.

08:05.070 --> 08:05.630
Zhi Hui,

08:06.360 --> 08:07.040
wake up.

08:08.800 --> 08:09.480
Wake up.

08:09.720 --> 08:10.480
We're home.

08:12.510 --> 08:13.190
Wake up.

08:13.560 --> 08:14.240
We're home.

08:23.800 --> 08:25.430
Goodbye, Ms. Lin. Goodbye, Coach.

08:25.430 --> 08:26.270
Be careful.

08:26.270 --> 08:27.400
Bye, Ms. Lin, Coach.

08:34.909 --> 08:36.360
Look, look.

08:36.750 --> 08:39.880
What a touching display
of a deep teacher-student bond.

08:40.510 --> 08:41.549
Isn't that heavy?

08:42.320 --> 08:43.360
Isn't he heavy?

08:44.510 --> 08:46.510
Coach, maybe you should put me down.

08:47.240 --> 08:49.440
Your ankle needs proper rest right now.

08:49.790 --> 08:51.240
Otherwise, it will cause permanent damage

08:51.240 --> 08:52.720
to your football career.

08:54.550 --> 08:55.750
Football career...

08:56.750 --> 08:57.440
Coach,

08:57.910 --> 08:58.630
do you think Wen Chengye

08:58.630 --> 09:00.760
even cares about his football career?

09:02.600 --> 09:03.930
What makes you ask that?

09:05.150 --> 09:06.630
The way he's been acting—

09:06.930 --> 09:08.170
going off on his own

09:08.200 --> 09:10.200
and ignoring the game plan.

09:12.120 --> 09:14.120
Was he trying to get back at the team?

09:14.670 --> 09:16.130
Or trying to get back at me?

09:16.910 --> 09:17.960
Get back at you?

09:19.670 --> 09:20.840
Are there

09:21.320 --> 09:24.380
any conflicts between you two
that we don't know about?

09:24.630 --> 09:25.390
No.

09:25.390 --> 09:26.750
I was just asking.

09:29.510 --> 09:31.030
I just think he doesn't take himself

09:31.030 --> 09:32.690
or football seriously at all.

09:37.630 --> 09:38.670
Oh, Ms. Lin,

09:39.200 --> 09:41.150
when we get to my home later,
can you tell my grandma

09:41.150 --> 09:43.150
I just twisted my ankle by accident?

09:43.240 --> 09:45.600
But you must update me
on your condition every day.

09:45.600 --> 09:46.840
If it hasn't gotten better,

09:46.840 --> 09:49.270
we'll need to go back to the hospital
for another checkup.

09:49.270 --> 09:51.240
Don't try to tough it out.

09:51.630 --> 09:52.750
Got it, Ms. Lin.

09:59.150 --> 10:01.200
What a day.

10:01.790 --> 10:04.250
But those kids had it even harder
than we did.

10:11.670 --> 10:13.270
How did it not occur to me

10:13.480 --> 10:15.440
that if it's downhill going there,

10:15.440 --> 10:17.870
it'll be uphill coming back?

10:18.840 --> 10:19.670
Tired?

10:20.210 --> 10:22.440
Tired and hungry.

10:25.200 --> 10:26.080
I'm okay.

10:28.840 --> 10:29.970
I can lend you a hand.

10:31.030 --> 10:32.320
I won't say no, then.

10:38.080 --> 10:39.750
I didn't think they could win,

10:40.630 --> 10:43.160
but I also didn't expect them
to lose so badly.

10:45.960 --> 10:47.460
That's just how cruel

10:47.910 --> 10:49.440
competitive sports can be.

10:51.960 --> 10:54.200
Do you regret leading them, Ms. Lin?

10:55.750 --> 10:56.550
Not at all.

10:57.150 --> 10:57.790
Then...

10:58.810 --> 11:00.470
are you thinking of giving up?

11:01.670 --> 11:02.910
Definitely not.

11:06.670 --> 11:09.000
We've still got a long uphill climb ahead.

11:09.320 --> 11:10.320
I'll pull you up.

11:23.550 --> 11:24.280
Do you think—

11:25.200 --> 11:26.930
with them so crushed like this—

11:27.440 --> 11:29.300
the team is just going to disband?

11:29.750 --> 11:31.000
Miss, sir,

11:31.000 --> 11:32.460
would you like a bracelet?

11:32.750 --> 11:34.120
Jasmine bracelets.

11:46.200 --> 11:48.600
Jasmine bracelets. They smell wonderful.

11:53.870 --> 11:56.210
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

11:56.510 --> 11:57.790
Why did you buy this?

11:56.850 --> 12:01.100
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

12:01.690 --> 12:03.650
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

12:04.170 --> 12:09.070
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
I chanced upon ♪

12:05.270 --> 12:06.390
Jasmine means

12:08.240 --> 12:09.660
"forever together, never apart."

12:09.660 --> 12:12.460
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

12:12.980 --> 12:16.400
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

12:17.030 --> 12:18.320
I've coached many teams.

12:17.370 --> 12:20.130
♪ I once dreamed of something beautiful ♪

12:19.840 --> 12:20.960
The real bonds

12:21.050 --> 12:25.170
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

12:21.510 --> 12:23.910
are often forged after the biggest fights.

12:24.120 --> 12:25.480
So, they won't disband.

12:25.850 --> 12:28.300
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

12:28.850 --> 12:33.020
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

12:33.540 --> 12:36.390
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

12:33.550 --> 12:34.320
Actually...

12:36.510 --> 12:37.550
there's another reason.

12:36.980 --> 12:40.790
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

12:38.150 --> 12:38.840
What is it?

12:40.790 --> 12:42.120
Because of you, Ms. Lin.

12:42.320 --> 12:44.360
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

12:42.670 --> 12:43.270
Me?

12:44.390 --> 12:46.030
You never forced them.

12:45.100 --> 12:48.850
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

12:47.200 --> 12:49.240
Instead, you gently helped them discover

12:49.240 --> 12:50.550
what they truly wanted and let them

12:50.150 --> 12:52.570
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

12:51.390 --> 12:53.240
choose to step onto the pitch themselves.

12:53.240 --> 12:56.950
♪ Still beautiful in its entirety ♪

12:54.390 --> 12:55.590
So for them, football

12:56.630 --> 12:57.630
isn't a business,

12:57.810 --> 13:00.340
♪ There's no need to seek a final answer ♪

12:58.320 --> 12:59.440
or a blood sport.

13:00.390 --> 13:01.960
Even after such a crushing defeat,

13:01.270 --> 13:05.040
♪ Let the ending remain with
questions unanswered ♪

13:02.910 --> 13:04.030
on the pitch,

13:04.630 --> 13:05.840
they still want to play

13:05.840 --> 13:08.410
♪ No need to prove it with promises ♪

13:06.270 --> 13:07.470
and still want to win.

13:09.390 --> 13:13.150
♪ The dusk when we once vowed
to stay together ♪

13:10.070 --> 13:11.140
Their hearts

13:11.790 --> 13:13.120
haven't left the pitch.

13:14.000 --> 13:16.430
♪ No need to cling to forever ♪

13:14.320 --> 13:15.580
So they won't disband.

13:16.940 --> 13:20.280
♪ Allow parting to happen quietly ♪

13:21.610 --> 13:24.110
♪ The inner voice hidden in the origami ♪

13:25.510 --> 13:27.550
Thank you, Wang Fa.

13:25.570 --> 13:30.970
♪ Each scratch and line
is proof of beauty ♪

13:29.030 --> 13:30.240
I have a request.

13:30.910 --> 13:31.480
Go ahead.

13:32.390 --> 13:34.390
I can help them keep playing.

13:36.200 --> 13:37.800
But you have to help them win.

13:44.390 --> 13:45.150
Deal.

14:32.030 --> 14:32.870
Tell me.

14:33.480 --> 14:34.480
Where did you go?

14:38.840 --> 14:40.840
I told you to meet with
the former admissions officer

14:40.840 --> 14:42.240
for a one-on-one consultation.

14:42.240 --> 14:44.240
All you had to do was show up and talk.

14:44.840 --> 14:46.670
Yet you actually stood them up!

14:56.240 --> 14:57.370
How did you get hurt?

14:58.320 --> 14:59.920
From playing football, huh?

15:00.870 --> 15:02.870
Have you lost your mind?

15:03.390 --> 15:04.540
Yes, I have.

15:04.750 --> 15:05.750
Say that again!

15:14.730 --> 15:15.720
Wen Chengye.

15:16.630 --> 15:18.120
I told you long ago—

15:19.000 --> 15:20.750
stop messing around
with that bottom-tier team.

15:20.750 --> 15:21.390
You just wouldn't listen.

15:21.390 --> 15:22.030
And now you're injured.

15:22.030 --> 15:23.390
How stupid are you?

15:24.870 --> 15:26.440
I applied to Berkeley for you
and put down

15:26.440 --> 15:28.240
computer science as your major.

15:28.320 --> 15:30.510
Including football on your application

15:30.510 --> 15:32.110
wouldn't even add much.

15:33.240 --> 15:34.030
You've got a great future ahead of you,

15:34.030 --> 15:36.080
so stop wasting time, okay?

15:37.150 --> 15:38.550
Then let it go to waste.

15:38.550 --> 15:40.200
I never wanted to study abroad anyway.

15:40.200 --> 15:41.510
You must go abroad!

15:45.270 --> 15:47.130
You're my son—Wen Ruigang's son.

15:47.560 --> 15:48.560
You'll do as I say.

15:51.320 --> 15:51.940
Right.

15:52.280 --> 15:53.510
I'm your son.

15:54.000 --> 15:55.440
If it weren't for that DNA test showing

15:55.440 --> 15:57.320
I might be your only son,

15:57.790 --> 15:58.860
I probably

15:59.080 --> 16:01.030
wouldn't mean anything to you.

16:03.200 --> 16:06.330
That test was only for
getting some documents reissued.

16:09.790 --> 16:10.960
Don't bring up

16:11.880 --> 16:13.040
the past again.

16:13.060 --> 16:14.440
Why can't I bring it up?

16:15.840 --> 16:17.700
How cold-blooded must a father be

16:18.270 --> 16:19.790
to take his son, who wasn't even 10,

16:19.790 --> 16:21.390
to get a DNA test?

16:25.150 --> 16:26.320
This is the one.

16:26.320 --> 16:27.200
Kid,

16:27.200 --> 16:29.440
in a bit, we're going to do
a mouth swab on you.

16:29.440 --> 16:31.570
Don't be afraid. Just open your mouth.

16:31.570 --> 16:32.500
Xu,

16:32.530 --> 16:33.390
take the sample.

16:33.390 --> 16:33.980
Okay.

16:34.030 --> 16:35.260
Because deep down,

16:35.290 --> 16:36.760
you've never cared about me.

16:36.760 --> 16:37.790
Not even a bit.

16:40.600 --> 16:42.200
I... I never cared about you?

16:44.550 --> 16:47.120
Wen Chengye, I've spent so much time

16:47.120 --> 16:48.960
and so much money
sending you to study abroad.

16:48.960 --> 16:50.840
And you say I never cared about you?

16:50.840 --> 16:52.170
Then listen carefully.

16:52.200 --> 16:54.930
I never wanted to study abroad
in the first place.

17:01.960 --> 17:03.290
Don't be so ungrateful.

17:03.440 --> 17:04.920
Look at your classmates.

17:05.310 --> 17:06.720
How many of them have what you have?

17:06.720 --> 17:07.440
And you don't even appreciate it?

17:07.440 --> 17:09.109
Did I ask for any of this?

17:09.109 --> 17:10.640
Never play football again.

17:11.000 --> 17:12.530
Never play football again!

17:54.880 --> 17:56.400
Kid! Kid!

17:56.400 --> 17:58.030
Whose child is he? He just fainted!

17:58.030 --> 17:59.000
-Kid!
-Son!

17:59.400 --> 17:59.920
Son!

18:00.400 --> 18:01.110
Son, are you alright?

18:01.110 --> 18:02.550
Doctor! Doctor!

18:02.550 --> 18:05.010
-Come with me! Hurry!
-He fainted! Where to?

18:45.110 --> 18:45.720
Wanxing,

18:46.310 --> 18:47.240
why are you here?

18:47.830 --> 18:48.960
To see you.

18:49.200 --> 18:51.860
Thank you for tutoring them
in math and physics.

18:52.310 --> 18:54.040
Wen Chengye didn't come today.

18:55.260 --> 18:55.950
I know.

18:56.350 --> 18:58.720
He probably won't be coming anymore.

18:59.270 --> 19:01.510
No wonder the class seemed so out of it.

19:02.030 --> 19:03.240
From what I gathered,

19:03.240 --> 19:04.960
they're looking for someone
to replace Wen Chengye

19:04.960 --> 19:06.620
but haven't found anyone yet.

19:11.590 --> 19:12.240
Here.

19:14.680 --> 19:15.810
For me?

19:17.110 --> 19:18.240
This is for you too.

19:19.600 --> 19:20.670
Come on, hop on.

19:20.690 --> 19:22.090
I'll take you somewhere.

19:22.240 --> 19:23.070
Where?

19:23.530 --> 19:24.770
You'll see.

19:38.640 --> 19:39.400
Here it is.

19:41.410 --> 19:42.940
Do you remember this place?

19:43.230 --> 19:44.430
Of course.

19:44.750 --> 19:46.640
Back in school, whenever we had a break,

19:46.640 --> 19:48.900
we'd come sit here for a whole afternoon.

19:49.250 --> 19:50.980
And sneak glances at cute guys.

19:52.680 --> 19:54.140
You were the one sneaking.

19:58.160 --> 19:58.830
Here.

20:03.090 --> 20:04.090
See that?

20:04.920 --> 20:05.920
Glove puppets.

20:12.750 --> 20:13.830
When we were kids,

20:13.830 --> 20:15.750
you loved watching glove puppet shows.

20:15.750 --> 20:17.350
I remember you used to
come over to my place all the time

20:17.350 --> 20:19.510
to watch the old man next door
carve wooden puppets.

20:19.510 --> 20:20.770
Do you still like them?

20:23.400 --> 20:25.330
I haven't played with them in ages.

20:28.000 --> 20:29.960
Happy New Year.

20:36.240 --> 20:44.960
The sun rises above this wilderness.

20:54.000 --> 20:55.730
This place has changed so much.

20:56.550 --> 20:57.510
Not that much.

20:58.000 --> 21:00.030
Aren't Ju Li and Lin Wanxing

21:00.030 --> 21:01.960
still sitting together, playing?

21:18.100 --> 21:18.700
Come here.

21:26.590 --> 21:27.790
Thank you, Li.

21:31.510 --> 21:32.120
Here?

21:32.920 --> 21:33.880
Come on, do it.

21:37.920 --> 21:39.400
Seal released.

21:42.400 --> 21:44.770
The past can never be changed

21:44.790 --> 21:46.070
or erased.

21:46.750 --> 21:49.280
But the future
will always be waiting for you.

21:51.990 --> 21:52.870
Don't worry.

21:53.400 --> 21:55.530
Lin Wanxing will keep moving forward.

21:57.750 --> 21:58.350
Good girl.

21:58.500 --> 22:00.010
Come on, let me walk you up.

22:07.750 --> 22:09.240
Looks like I won't have to.

22:22.790 --> 22:24.720
-Bye.
-Be careful on your way home.

22:27.960 --> 22:29.020
Out for a night run?

22:29.780 --> 22:30.510
No.

22:33.750 --> 22:34.750
You're back late.

22:40.480 --> 22:42.030
Li saw I wasn't in a good mood,

22:42.030 --> 22:43.430
so she took me somewhere.

22:45.510 --> 22:46.770
Still because of them?

22:48.400 --> 22:49.930
Worried about their uncertain future?

22:49.930 --> 22:52.100
♪ Two souls aligned ♪

22:51.200 --> 22:51.890
Well,

22:52.440 --> 22:54.070
any words of wisdom, Mr. Coach?

22:53.800 --> 22:55.720
♪ In silent gravity ♪

22:57.950 --> 23:00.080
♪ Heal my heart ♪

23:00.700 --> 23:03.210
♪ With every part of you ♪

23:03.000 --> 23:04.070
It's flickering.

23:04.750 --> 23:06.640
Just pretend it's a star.

23:05.890 --> 23:07.780
♪ Our words flow ♪

23:07.240 --> 23:07.960
Make a wish.

23:09.360 --> 23:11.360
♪ A gentle stream ♪

23:13.670 --> 23:15.850
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

23:16.500 --> 23:19.020
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

23:21.230 --> 23:27.140
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

23:24.240 --> 23:25.160
I wish

23:25.620 --> 23:27.220
our team could come together

23:28.030 --> 23:29.510
and that we could all make it
to the next round.

23:29.060 --> 23:30.680
♪ We trace the roads ♪

23:30.240 --> 23:31.550
I don't want to give up.

23:31.460 --> 23:34.570
♪ That never see an end ♪

23:37.250 --> 23:40.660
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

23:41.450 --> 23:46.060
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

23:46.720 --> 23:50.690
♪ And wake the warmth inside ♪

23:52.450 --> 23:54.870
♪ Life begins alone ♪

23:55.590 --> 23:58.500
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

24:00.200 --> 24:02.610
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

24:01.230 --> 24:01.520
[Receive Money by QR Code]

24:01.670 --> 24:01.890
[Loading]

24:01.980 --> 24:02.450
[Pay]

24:03.220 --> 24:06.660
♪ To light our way back home ♪

24:07.240 --> 24:09.230
Then, thank you, Coach Wang.

24:08.770 --> 24:10.470
♪ True love is not just ♪

24:09.250 --> 24:10.050
Come on.

24:10.080 --> 24:11.230
Let's not head home just yet.

24:11.230 --> 24:12.830
♪ The gaze when two hearts first meet ♪

24:11.520 --> 24:13.120
I want to take you somewhere.

24:13.740 --> 24:17.730
♪ It's courage in the arms ♪

24:19.110 --> 24:19.880
Grandma.

24:23.350 --> 24:24.440
Teachers.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.070
Sorry to bother you, Grandma.

24:26.070 --> 24:28.200
We came to have a chat with Fu Xinshu.

24:29.200 --> 24:30.150
He's inside.

24:30.350 --> 24:31.270
Go on in.

24:31.510 --> 24:32.640
Thank you, Grandma.

24:32.970 --> 24:33.770
Excuse us.

24:37.590 --> 24:38.720
How's your ankle?

24:39.400 --> 24:40.200
Much better.

24:42.750 --> 24:43.920
Actually, today

24:43.920 --> 24:46.050
we have something to discuss with you.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.640
Qin Ao and the others

24:49.000 --> 24:50.790
are planning to give up on Wen Chengye

24:50.790 --> 24:52.850
and find another substitute player.

24:55.440 --> 24:56.500
Ms. Lin, actually,

24:57.720 --> 24:59.590
I've already thought about this.

25:00.640 --> 25:01.440
Honestly, I don't really care

25:01.440 --> 25:03.240
whether he bumped me on purpose.

25:03.400 --> 25:06.460
What I want to know is
whether he actually wanted to win.

25:07.410 --> 25:08.400
I don't want to play football

25:08.400 --> 25:10.460
with someone who doesn't want to win.

25:11.480 --> 25:13.480
It'll only drag the whole team down.

25:14.400 --> 25:15.270
We'll talk about that later

25:15.270 --> 25:17.030
during the team review.

25:18.070 --> 25:19.510
Ms. Lin and I came today

25:19.510 --> 25:21.310
to ask you about something else.

25:22.790 --> 25:24.520
Is there some unresolved issue

25:25.270 --> 25:26.960
between you and Wen Chengye?

25:30.510 --> 25:32.640
I've been watching you two for a while.

25:33.510 --> 25:35.830
Wen Chengye clearly cares a lot about you,

25:35.830 --> 25:36.890
but at the same time

25:37.160 --> 25:39.490
seems to have some grievance against you.

25:42.400 --> 25:43.330
Fu Xinshu,

25:43.350 --> 25:44.810
tell us the truth.

25:45.000 --> 25:46.400
Before the match,

25:46.700 --> 25:49.500
did something happen
between you and Wen Chengye?

25:50.310 --> 25:51.770
What I also want to know is—

25:52.030 --> 25:54.110
why is it so easy for you to set him off?

25:59.000 --> 26:01.600
Actually, it all goes back to
when we were kids.

26:08.440 --> 26:10.370
Since it was his birthday that day,

26:11.310 --> 26:12.350
why didn't you go?

26:15.200 --> 26:15.640
Be...

26:17.200 --> 26:18.960
Because that day, my...

26:21.270 --> 26:22.070
my parents...

26:24.960 --> 26:25.750
It's okay.

26:28.310 --> 26:29.310
If it's too hard to say,

26:29.310 --> 26:30.840
then don't force yourself.

26:31.830 --> 26:34.090
But there's something I want you to know.

26:34.310 --> 26:36.270
Wen Chengye joined the team—

26:36.720 --> 26:38.120
and keeps targeting you—

26:39.270 --> 26:41.470
for more than just his love of football.

26:42.200 --> 26:45.060
A big part of it is
that he's waiting for your answer.

26:47.160 --> 26:48.690
He wants an answer from you.

26:51.680 --> 26:53.340
It's really important to him.

26:55.480 --> 26:57.880
Ms. Lin, I know you're about to say

26:57.880 --> 27:00.680
that he must have his own reasons
for not saying it.

27:01.450 --> 27:03.890
But today, I'm here
to push you, Fu Xinshu.

27:06.200 --> 27:08.600
Wen Chengye really cares about that "why."

27:08.650 --> 27:10.270
He's not a sociopath.

27:10.680 --> 27:13.000
He's just paranoid and lonely.

27:18.630 --> 27:19.740
Your silence

27:21.070 --> 27:22.200
is very cruel to him.

27:28.790 --> 27:30.680
Fu Xinshu, I know

27:30.680 --> 27:33.210
you're the one
who wants the best for the team.

27:33.270 --> 27:34.160
If you don't want to say,

27:34.160 --> 27:35.890
I'm sure you have your reasons.

27:36.200 --> 27:37.480
But the day you got hurt,

27:37.480 --> 27:39.080
he was hurt pretty badly too.

27:39.270 --> 27:40.510
And he still rushed to the hospital

27:40.510 --> 27:41.790
to wait for your news.

27:46.410 --> 27:48.240
If you guys have the chance,

27:48.310 --> 27:50.840
you two should sit down
and have a proper talk.

28:14.440 --> 28:15.400
Rest early.

28:15.750 --> 28:17.210
Don't dwell on it tonight.

28:19.750 --> 28:20.550
How about...

28:21.560 --> 28:22.850
we grab a drink?

28:35.810 --> 28:38.270
Fu Xinshu still
wouldn't tell us the reason.

28:39.920 --> 28:41.480
Maybe it's just too heavy

28:41.590 --> 28:42.550
for him.

28:44.200 --> 28:47.280
But as long as Wen Chengye's grievance
remains unresolved,

28:47.280 --> 28:48.440
the team will always be

28:48.440 --> 28:50.200
sitting on a ticking time bomb.

28:52.750 --> 28:55.120
We can't keep pushing Xinshu either.

28:55.280 --> 28:56.490
If we push him any harder,

28:56.490 --> 28:58.220
he'll only shut down even more.

29:01.400 --> 29:03.440
We'll have to find another way.

29:07.720 --> 29:09.520
Maybe we need to get them to stop.

29:10.700 --> 29:12.270
Stop focusing on their opponents

29:12.270 --> 29:14.110
and stop dwelling on old grudges.

29:14.110 --> 29:15.110
Just look back

29:15.750 --> 29:19.410
and think about why they stepped
onto the pitch in the first place.

29:24.160 --> 29:25.890
"Never forget why you started,

29:26.590 --> 29:28.050
and you'll reach the end."

29:32.030 --> 29:33.030
I'll give it a try.

29:33.550 --> 29:34.750
Let me say something.

29:38.690 --> 29:42.150
[Little Savage Tribe]

29:38.950 --> 29:41.110
Everyone, I want you to complete
a reflection assignment.

29:41.110 --> 29:43.640
Answer this question
with complete honesty:

29:43.830 --> 29:46.260
Why do you play football?

29:46.660 --> 29:48.240
You have a week

29:48.240 --> 29:49.370
to give me an answer.

29:57.770 --> 29:59.690
I hope it works.

30:13.200 --> 30:14.650
Guess they're not coming

30:14.810 --> 30:16.270
while we're down a player.

30:18.680 --> 30:20.940
And no one even turned in the assignment.

30:21.210 --> 30:22.860
That did nothing at all.

30:24.590 --> 30:25.590
Understandable.

30:26.270 --> 30:28.680
A team of 10 isn't really a complete team.

30:34.470 --> 30:34.670
[Group B Round 3 Match Schedule;
This Sunday]

30:34.690 --> 30:35.010
[at 2 PM, Hongjing No. 8 High School
vs. Chuncheng Xinpeng.]

30:35.150 --> 30:38.660
[Round 3; Group B Group Stage]

30:40.320 --> 30:41.510
[Group B Group Stage]

30:41.530 --> 30:44.480
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
vs. Chuncheng Xinpeng]

30:45.030 --> 30:48.160
The date for the match
against Chuncheng Xinpeng is set.

30:51.930 --> 30:53.930
If we only have 10 players,

30:53.950 --> 30:55.110
are we bound to lose?

30:57.050 --> 31:00.160
Especially when the team is so divided.

31:04.410 --> 31:05.440
Leave it to me,

31:05.460 --> 31:06.260
Ms. Lin.

31:10.440 --> 31:13.930
[Little Savage Tribe]

31:10.850 --> 31:12.480
Everyone to the field. Now.

31:35.160 --> 31:35.960
Hello, Coach.

31:35.970 --> 31:36.710
Coach.

31:36.750 --> 31:37.510
-Hello, Coach.
-Hello, Coach.

31:37.510 --> 31:38.840
-Hello, Coach.
-Coach.

31:40.400 --> 31:41.070
Coach,

31:41.350 --> 31:43.270
we've already seen the schedule.

31:43.290 --> 31:45.290
If we lose again, we're out for good.

31:45.440 --> 31:47.680
With just 10 of us,
there's no way we can win.

31:47.680 --> 31:48.350
Maybe...

31:48.880 --> 31:50.510
we should just stop training.

31:50.510 --> 31:51.920
We suck.

32:05.090 --> 32:05.640
Come on.

32:06.050 --> 32:07.290
Play a match with me.

32:13.920 --> 32:15.050
Press him over here!

32:16.230 --> 32:16.960
Go, Coach!

32:16.960 --> 32:17.400
Carry us!

32:17.400 --> 32:18.920
Close him down! Close him down!

32:18.920 --> 32:19.920
I can't stop him!

32:19.920 --> 32:20.960
I've got it; I'll cover.

32:20.960 --> 32:21.990
Me too!

32:22.790 --> 32:24.090
Coach, I'm behind you!

32:26.720 --> 32:27.960
Coach is a beast!

32:28.480 --> 32:30.280
-Let's double-team him.
-Okay!

32:32.400 --> 32:33.930
-Coach, take the pass!
-Go!

32:34.750 --> 32:36.240
Coach is ridiculously good!

32:36.240 --> 32:37.240
I can't catch him!

32:37.750 --> 32:39.340
Feng Suo, you're up!

32:40.550 --> 32:42.240
We won!

33:21.680 --> 33:22.510
Over to you!

33:23.170 --> 33:24.930
Quick! Stop the coach!

33:25.480 --> 33:26.310
So fast!

33:29.110 --> 33:29.960
Nice shot!

33:31.510 --> 33:34.370
-Nice shot!
-Feels like we got carried, doesn't it?

33:40.240 --> 33:41.200
Coach is way too fast.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.160
I can't even react.

33:42.160 --> 33:43.350
Coach is seriously incredible.

33:43.350 --> 33:44.200
He's impossible to defend.

33:44.200 --> 33:45.400
Totally impossible.

33:46.200 --> 33:47.680
Coach, that goal was amazing.

33:47.680 --> 33:48.480
So awesome, Coach!

33:48.480 --> 33:50.310
Coach doesn't even need us to
cover for him when he attacks.

33:50.310 --> 33:52.070
If our team had someone like him,

33:52.070 --> 33:53.720
how could we have lost
to Yongchuan Hengjiu?

33:53.720 --> 33:55.520
Coach should just play forward.

33:56.070 --> 33:57.330
Who are you talking to?

33:57.720 --> 33:59.580
We already have someone like him.

34:00.400 --> 34:01.730
Are you kidding me, bro?

34:08.880 --> 34:10.909
Looks like Fu Xinshu gets it now.

34:11.480 --> 34:12.400
I've got the game tape ready.

34:12.400 --> 34:14.860
Take your time watching it
when you get back.

34:27.920 --> 34:30.980
Everyone, look at
Wen Chengye's movement off the ball.

34:37.670 --> 34:39.150
He didn't seem to be kicking randomly.

34:39.150 --> 34:40.710
-He did it himself...
-He quickly anticipated

34:40.710 --> 34:42.030
the opponent's next move.

34:42.030 --> 34:43.290
-Yeah.
-Seems like...

34:43.920 --> 34:46.320
the same movement Coach used today, right?

34:49.360 --> 34:51.010
If we'd passed the ball to him then,

34:51.010 --> 34:52.420
wouldn't we have scored?

35:06.590 --> 35:08.120
Crashed into him that hard?

35:32.550 --> 35:33.980
My foot!

35:34.360 --> 35:35.760
-Fu!
-Fu!

35:43.550 --> 35:46.010
-He jumped to block the ball?
-Seems like it.

35:46.030 --> 35:48.230
Did he really not notice
Fu was charging in too?

35:48.230 --> 35:49.070
-Yeah.
-Probably not.

35:49.070 --> 35:50.600
Then we misunderstood him.

35:50.880 --> 35:52.000
His last kick

35:52.440 --> 35:53.890
didn't seem intentional, right?

35:53.890 --> 35:55.270
Definitely not.

35:55.880 --> 35:57.840
When Wen Chengye
took that hit in the first half,

35:57.840 --> 36:00.150
it looked like he was injured
just as badly as Fu.

36:00.150 --> 36:00.710
True.

36:02.800 --> 36:03.480
Well.

36:03.480 --> 36:05.320
Then why didn't he say anything?

36:06.550 --> 36:07.590
Because even if he had,

36:07.590 --> 36:08.800
none of us would've listened.

36:08.800 --> 36:09.710
So why bother?

36:10.670 --> 36:13.110
I was so nice to him
during that "vegetable-planting" drill.

36:13.110 --> 36:14.840
We even dragged him
to take photos together, right?

36:14.840 --> 36:15.360
Right.

36:15.760 --> 36:16.590
Indeed.

36:19.760 --> 36:20.820
It's because of me.

36:22.880 --> 36:24.190
What does it have to do with you, Fu?

36:24.190 --> 36:25.920
Stop making it about yourself.

36:37.480 --> 36:39.140
Let's bring Wen Chengye back.

36:39.440 --> 36:40.900
I'll go find him tomorrow.

36:41.550 --> 36:43.010
I'll go talk to him myself.

36:57.230 --> 36:58.190
I'm sorry.

37:04.180 --> 37:06.380
If that's all, I'm going back to eating.

37:06.610 --> 37:08.800
C-Can we talk outside?

37:09.440 --> 37:10.900
I'll wait for you outside.

37:25.320 --> 37:25.850
Go ahead.

37:28.000 --> 37:29.110
Well...

37:29.790 --> 37:31.390
Can you come back to the team?

37:31.920 --> 37:33.360
We all know now.

37:33.360 --> 37:35.270
You weren't playing recklessly before.

37:35.270 --> 37:36.530
We misunderstood you.

37:37.320 --> 37:39.250
Everyone feels terrible about it.

37:41.880 --> 37:44.800
So you're here on everyone's behalf,
asking me to come back?

37:44.800 --> 37:45.590
Come back.

37:45.800 --> 37:46.920
The team needs you.

37:49.920 --> 37:51.400
I see. Without me on the team,

37:51.400 --> 37:52.840
your dumb teammates
were struggling so much

37:52.840 --> 37:54.360
they couldn't even keep playing,

37:54.360 --> 37:56.590
and that's why you came to
ask me to come back.

37:56.590 --> 37:57.840
They're not dumb.

38:02.480 --> 38:03.030
Right.

38:03.880 --> 38:04.880
They're not dumb.

38:05.400 --> 38:06.330
I'm the dumb one.

38:08.230 --> 38:09.000
Give up.

38:10.000 --> 38:11.190
I'm not coming back.

38:11.550 --> 38:12.480
Wen Chengye,

38:12.800 --> 38:13.480
if you're still hung up

38:13.480 --> 38:15.070
on what happened between us as kids...

38:15.070 --> 38:17.110
You wouldn't say a word before,
no matter what.

38:17.110 --> 38:20.240
But now, for their sake,
you're willing to talk about it?

38:24.960 --> 38:26.220
I don't want to hear it.

38:30.230 --> 38:31.000
Wen Chengye!

38:31.000 --> 38:31.610
Let go!

38:37.360 --> 38:39.160
Didn't you already give up on me?

38:48.960 --> 38:49.840
I'm sorry.

38:51.440 --> 38:52.230
Qin Ao,

38:52.560 --> 38:55.070
where's that fire you had
when you wanted to hit me?

38:55.070 --> 38:56.480
Softening up now?

38:57.710 --> 38:58.920
Coward.

39:26.100 --> 39:27.380
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

39:28.570 --> 39:29.900
♪ Because you're with me ♪

39:33.050 --> 39:34.200
♪ The light shimmers ♪

39:35.750 --> 39:36.810
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪
